Snake Neon 2026 (ZMEIKA Online) - Online action web game, inspired by Taneli Armanto, recreated by Russian developers Axyonov Nazar, Vladimir Gartsev, Leonid Kurov,
Nikita Ermakov. 

Terms of use:
1. Section 107 of the Copyright Act gives examples of purposes that are favored by fair use: “criticism, comment, news reporting, teaching (including multiple copies
for classroom use), scholarship, research.” Use for one of these purposes is not automatically fair, and uses for other purposes can be fair. The statute lays 
out four factors to consider in deciding whether a particular use is fair.
