User functionality:
1. Basically, this game contains 3 sites. "index" is an entry site, greeting user with quick description of the game and quick play button.
2. Game itself contains simple playing scenario (borderless), using WASD or arrows to move the snake
3. Death redirects you to "death.html" page with your saved score. There, you may save your score and share it in leaderboard with other players.
4. Button "Replay" send you back in the game.
5. Button "Leaderboard" is a data site where your progress is saved and could be shared with other people. 

Code language used:
* JavaScript (ECMAScript 2024 (ES2024))
* HTML5 

Programs involved in creation of this game and site:
* Microsoft Visual Studio 2022

Budget of the game: 2 cola cans, 1 energy drink and 2 fills of vape liquid.
